data.name: ReadHealthInsuranceAvailability1
data.value: select INSURANCE_ID, POLICY_NUMBER, GROUP_NUMBER, INSURANCE_NAME, STREET_1, STREET_2, CITY, [STATE], ZIP_5, ZIP_4, COST, COST_FREQUENCY, VERIFIED_DATE, END_DATE, EMPLOYER_NAME, EMP_STREET_1, EMP_STREET_2, EMP_CITY, EMP_STATE, EMP_ZIP_5, EMP_ZIP_4, EMP_AREA_CODE, EMP_PHONE_NO, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPD_TSTAMP, CSP_NUMBER from CKT_HEALTH_INS_AV where (CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (INSURANCE_ID > @insuranceId) order by INSURANCE_ID
